@section Operating Systems

This section describes problems that have occured while porting the
package to various operating systems.

@menu
* SCO-322::         SCO Unix 3.2.2 (ODT 1.0 / 1.1)
* SCO-324::         SCO Unix 3.2.4 (ODT 2.0)
